# Automation Layer: The "Overseer" Engine

This directory contains the protocols and logic for the **Autonomous Supervisor** agent. Its purpose is to reduce human intervention by automating standard approvals and maintaining the momentum of Sprint execution.

## ðŸ†• Sprint Supervisor (Python-Based Automation)

**NEW!** Complete Python implementation untuk autonomous sprint execution dan pengawasan.

### Quick Start
```bash
# Check sprint status
python supervisor_cli.py status

# Start continuous execution
python supervisor_cli.py start

# Test approval engine
python supervisor_cli.py approve --command "npm run test"
```

