## Original Structure

1.  **`supervisor_protocol.md`**: The brain of the automation. Defines *when* to interrupt the user and *when* to proceed autonomously.
2.  **`approval_policy.md`**: Strict logic gates for "Safe Auto-Approval".
3.  **`loop_controller.md`**: The state machine for continuous sprint execution.

## Usage

To invoke the Supervisor:
> "Entrust this session to the Automation Layer. Begin continuous execution."

The Agent will then switch to **Supervisor Mode**, reading `supervisor_protocol.md` before every step.
